t-borne viruses. Considering these limitations, we propose strategies to bridge the existing gaps in the near future.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Wallau, Gabriel Luz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Barbier, Eder", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tomazatos, Alexandru", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schmidt-Chanasit, Jonas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bernard, Enrico", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "He, Biao", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d3fce26bc010f5c305d74047581f4b74", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9d67eda03785bfb3f9d65d67a4ecb5d7da95db22e601c91d568332255064f58e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/LN9KZ4AA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/LN9KZ4AA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/d358545aa82975451ee97f2c43bc8a61!/b36969-39430", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "e04077-22", "title": "Microbiology Spectrum", "volume": "11"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d3fce26bc010f5c305d74047581f4b74"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:LN9KZ4AA"}, {"identifier": "10.1128/spectrum.04077-22"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosysli